            "title": "台股全日回升1.94% 再創新高",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">台股經過昨天稍為回吐後，今日重現升勢並再創新高；台灣加權指數企穩31000點以上收市，報31408點，漲598點或1.94%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15587335-%e5%8f%b0%e8%82%a1%e5%85%a8%e6%97%a5%e5%9b%9e%e5%8d%871-94-%e5%86%8d%e5%89%b5%e6%96%b0%e9%ab%98",
