        {
            "title": "中信資源售美國鋁業股權 作價相等19.27億港元 股份午後復牌抽升",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中信資源(01205)公布，出售所持美國鋁業股份，作價2.47億美元，相等於約19.27億港元。該股午後復牌應聲抽升。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">該股復牌初段曾見0.5元，飆21.95%；截至下午約1時03分壣0.475元，漲15.85%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15587157-%e4%b8%ad%e4%bf%a1%e8%b3%87%e6%ba%90%e5%94%ae%e7%be%8e%e5%9c%8b%e9%8b%81%e6%a5%ad%e8%82%a1%e6%ac%8a-%e4%bd%9c%e5%83%b9%e7%9b%b8%e7%ad%8919-27%e5%84%84%e6%b8%af%e5%85%83-%e8%82%a1%e4%bb%bd%e5%8d%88",
