        {
            "title": "滬深A股早市反覆爭持 「三桶油」捱沽 保險股偏軟",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地股市今早先揚後回順，滬深兩市均曾倒跌並於早市後段呈好淡爭持。國際油價回落，「三桶油」自然受壓，保險股亦向淡。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/20200413-CH-石油輸出國組織_FB-1-1-1-1-3-1-1-1-2-3-1-1_source-ap_.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/20200413-CH-石油輸出國組織_FB-1-1-1-1-3-1-1-1-2-3-1-1_source-ap_.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上證綜指今早高開14點並於初段再上層樓，一度將升幅擴大至27點、高見4140點，在多番試高卻未能突破之下終於掉頭，於上午約10時開始倒跌，展開窄幅好淡爭持局面，半日低位4100點時倒跌11點；滬指中午收報4103點，跌9點或0.22%，半日成交8653.45億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成指亦呈好淡爭持，高開67點後升幅最多擴大至117點，於初段做出半日高位14424點，其後反覆回吐並曾在中段倒跌最多39點，最低報14266點，後段稍作反彈後再回軟；深指中午收報14293點，跌13點或0.1%，成交1.12萬億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300指數也跌7點或0.15%，收報4744點；創業板指數跌不足1點或0.01%，報3367點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-10.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-10.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">市場對美國向伊朗採取軍事行動憂慮緩和，國際油價昨天跌逾4%，「三桶油」A股今早全線向下。中國石化1(00386)A股(600028.SH)跌1.85%，報5.84元；中國海油(00883)A股(600938.SH)跌1.76%，報29.51元；中國石油(00857)A股(601857.SH)亦跌1.2%，報9.85元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">重磅保險股遍軟，中國平安(02318)A(601318.SH)跌1.41%，報66.46元；中國太保(02601)A股(601601.SH)跌1.76%，報44.13元；中國人壽(02628)A股(601628.SH)更挫2.42%，報47.65元。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"中國平安集團簡介 (來源：中國平安官網)\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20240708_FI_source-web_02318-Intro.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"中國平安集團簡介 (來源：中國平安官網)\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20240708_FI_source-web_02318-Intro.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">中國平安集團簡介 (來源：中國平安官網)</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">個別半導體相關股搶上，天岳先進(02631)A股(600234.SH)急飆，上午臨收市前終升近20%封板，報111.19元；峰岹科技(01304)A股(688279.SH)升9.59%，報223.02元；兆易創新(03986)A股(603986.SH)升7.08%，報273.02元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15586940-%e6%bb%ac%e6%b7%b1a%e8%82%a1%e6%97%a9%e5%b8%82%e5%8f%8d%e8%a6%86%e7%88%ad%e6%8c%81-%e3%80%8c%e4%b8%89%e6%a1%b6%e6%b2%b9%e3%80%8d%e6%8d%b1%e6%b2%bd-%e4%bf%9d%e9%9a%aa%e8%82%a1%e5%81%8f%e8%bb%9f",
